OL,3,CPaddington The Musical triumphs at
OL,4,CWhatsOnStage awards with nine wins
OL,6,FIt was a successful night for
OL,7,F'Paddington The Musical' winning the
OL,8,Fmost awards any new musical ever has
OL,9,Fat the WhatsonStage awards.
OL,11,FThe show won nine awards in total-
OL,12,F best direction, set design, best new
OL,13,Fmusical, costume design, sound design,
OL,14,Fhair, wig and make-up, musical
OL,15,Fsupervision/direction, casting, and
OL,16,Fbest professional debut performance
OL,17,Ffor Timi Akinyosade who plays Tony.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
