OL,3,CPaddington The Musical triumphs at
OL,4,CWhatsOnStage awards with nine wins
OL,6,FThe smash-hit musical, which stars a
OL,7,Flife-like puppet Paddington Bear,
OL,8,Fequalled Harry Potter And The Cursed
OL,9,FChild and Miss Saigon as the
OL,10,Fproduction with the most wins in the
OL,11,Fhistory of the awards show ` the most
OL,12,Ffor any new musical.
OL,14,FSince opening in December, it has
OL,15,Freceived rave reviews ` notably for
OL,16,Fbringing to life the famous bear
OL,17,Fthrough a two-person team consisting
OL,18,Fof James Hameed as remote puppeteer
OL,19,Fcontrolling the expressions and
OL,20,Fdelivering the voice, and Arti Shah
OL,21,Fembodying the character on stage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
