OL,3,CPaddington The Musical triumphs at
OL,4,CWhatsOnStage awards with nine wins
OL,6,FDarius Thompson and Alex Wood from
OL,7,FWhatsOnStage said: "The voters really
OL,8,Fdid look after that bear. Paddington's
OL,9,Frecord-setting awards haul has firmly
OL,10,Fcemented it as a fan-favourite new
OL,11,Faddition to the West End."
OL,13,FThe theatre awards ceremony also saw
OL,14,FEvita star Rachel Zegler and Richard
OL,15,FII actor Jonathan Bailey win the best
OL,16,Fperformer gongs for their respective
OL,17,Fcategories.
