OL,3,CPaddington The Musical triumphs at
OL,4,CWhatsOnStage awards with nine wins
OL,6,FRachel Zegler's performance included
OL,7,Ftreating West End passers-by to a
OL,8,Frendition of Don't Cry For Me
OL,9,FArgentina, as she belted the song over
OL,10,Fa balcony from the London Palladium
OL,11,Ftheatre.
OL,13,FEvita took home five awards, including
OL,14,Fbest musical revival and choreography.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
