OL,3,CPaddington The Musical triumphs at
OL,4,CWhatsOnStage awards with nine wins
OL,6,FFormer Love Island star and recent BBC
OL,7,FStrictly Come Dancing finalist Amber
OL,8,FDavies won the best supporting
OL,9,Fperformer in a musical award for
OL,10,Fplaying Jordan Baker in The Great
OL,11,FGatsby. Meanwhile author and Celebrity
OL,12,FTraitors star Sir Stephen Fry was
OL,13,Fnamed the best supporting performer in
OL,14,Fa play with his portrayal of Lady
OL,15,FBracknell in The Importance Of Being
OL,16,FEarnest.
