OL,3,CPaddington The Musical triumphs at
OL,4,CWhatsOnStage awards with nine wins
OL,6,FThe night also saw Dear England
OL,7,Fplaywright James Graham recognised
OL,8,Fwith the services to UK Theatre award,
OL,9,Fwhile Les Miserables won the best West
OL,10,FEnd show award.
